#: package/contents/ui/adapters/anthropic.js:36
msgid ""
"Anthropic enables extended thinking when effort is not Off, using the token "
"budget below. Temperature is forced to max while thinking."
msgstr ""
"Anthropic enables extended thinking when effort is not Off, using the token "
"budget below. Temperature is forced to max while thinking."

"Anthropic habilita el pensamiento extendido cuando el esfuerzo no está "
"desactivado, utilizando el presupuesto de tokens a continuación. La "
"temperatura se fuerza al máximo durante el razonamiento."

