#: package/contents/ui/adapters/openai.js:33
msgid ""
"Reasoning effort (low / medium / high) gates extended thinking. To see "
"thoughts on OpenAI / Poe / OpenRouter / Azure, enable Use Responses API; "
"chat-completions providers (DeepSeek, Qwen) surface reasoning via "
"reasoning_content."
msgstr ""
"Reasoning effort (low / medium / high) gates extended thinking. To see "
"thoughts on OpenAI / Poe / OpenRouter / Azure, enable Use Responses API; "
"chat-completions providers (DeepSeek, Qwen) surface reasoning via "
"reasoning_content."

"El esfuerzo de razonamiento (bajo / medio / alto) controla el pensamiento "
"extendido. Para ver los pensamientos en OpenAI / Poe / OpenRouter / Azure, "
"habilite 'Usar API de Responses'; los proveedores de chat-completions "
"(DeepSeek, Qwen) muestran el razonamiento a través de reasoning_content."

